-XGikGuWGdcxahjQXxJ6bEw">Sinh cư loạn thế - 生居亂世</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khi%E1%BA%BFu-N%C4%83ng-T%C4%A9nh/author-0k6qEpgf02Latsw5cZPrXg">Khiếu Năng Tĩnh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4ng-B%E1%BA%A3n-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/S%C6%A1n-c%C6%B0-b%C3%A1ch-v%E1%BB%8Bnh-k%E1%BB%B3-055/poem-k2QXRPAcka8SG3I_7IpRWQ">Sơn cư bách vịnh kỳ 055 - 山居百詠其五十五</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4ng-B%E1%BA%A3n-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/author-jnvtlp5PrNS3FoOBBGt7-w">Tông Bản thiền sư</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/Th%E1%BB%A9-v%E1%BA%ADn-t%C4%83ng-Ti%E1%BB%81m-ki%E1%BA%BFn-t%E1%BA%B7ng/poem-hz8hbWcAgwn0l_l-89-sBw">Thứ vận tăng Tiềm kiến tặng - 次韻僧潛見贈</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/author-ZsPeAEZWTH-jxxg2cYfLgg">Tô Thức</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Chi%C3%AAm-%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng/%E1%BB%A8c-t%C3%ADch-s%C6%A1n-c%C6%B0/poem-yezq_vKXfawT8Q8cIlAS9A">Ức tích sơn cư - 憶昔山居</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Chi%C3%AAm-%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng/author-CF4h4cy0l6rugNx2hdZfpQ">Chiêm Đồng</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ngu%E1%BB%B5-Tr%C6%B0ng/Xu%E1%BA%A5t-quan/poem-l_XCV4jE0JxCSKvcF-D5EQ">Xuất quan - 出關</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ngu%E1%BB%B5-Tr%C6%B0ng/author-etbB3Ex07HzNoQP-CZPmVA">Nguỵ Trưng</a>)<br></div>	</div>
